<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.9">
<l>matayāṉai pōleḻunta māmukilkāḷ vēṅkaṭattaip</l>
<l>patiyāka vāḻvīrkāḷ pāmpaṇaiyāṉ vārttaiyeṉṉē</l>
<l>katiyeṉṟun tāṉāvāṉ karutātōr peṇkoṭiyai</l>
<l>vataiceytā ṉeṉṉuñcol vaiyakattār matiyārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O clouds that rise like an elephant in rut! O you who flourish</l>
<l rend="indent">With Vēṅkaṭam as [your] place of residence!</l>
<l>What are the words of the [Lord] whose bed is a snake?</l>
<l>The people of the world will not respect [Him after hearing] the words</l>
<l>that He murdered a creeper[-like] tender woman,</l>
<l rend="indent">not remembering that He is always [her] refuge!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
